---
title: Cheesy Crumbed Courgette & Potato Wedges with Radish Salad & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: The herby mayo is going to be use two-fold tonight. Dip in either the golden crumbed courgette or the potato wedges. You know, we think both should get their turn. If you’re licking your fingers afterwards, don’t worry we did the same thing when these first hit the table.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
